#!markdown

### Examples - Edits API

#!markdown

* Definition: Given a prompt and an instruction, the model will return an edited version of the prompt
* Reference: https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/edits

#!pwsh

ai "tp 5 us states with most people with 2020 population and their capitals in json"

#!pwsh

Get-OpenAIEdit "powershell code get tp 5 us states with most people with 2020 population and their capitals in json" -Instruction "fix the spelling mistakes"

#!pwsh

Get-OpenAIEdit "powershell code get tp 5 us states with most people with 2020 population and their capitals in json" -Instruction "fix the spelling mistakes" -edits 3

#!pwsh

ai "use powershell regex, validate text as being a valid email address"

#!pwsh

ai "powershell code get the top 5 us states with most people with 2020 population"

#!pwsh

ai "powershell code get the top 5 us states with most people with 2020 population" -max_tokens 2000

